            "detailed_description": "<u>Game description</u><br><br>Flowing Lights is a mini-boss fights single stick shooter. Solve fine-tuned handcrafted combats that will test your reflexes and your tactical thinking. Challenge yourself in a fair, easy to learn/difficult to master shoot’em up.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Only intense, bite-size fights with unlimited retries: no frustration from restarting far away, no need to memorize a whole level,  just improve your skills at each try!<br></li><li>A new dodging and controlling experience! Take advantage of physics while sliding between bullets; anticipate gravity curved trajectories, not only straight lines!<br></li><li>Handcrafted fights and level design, each combat situation is fresh and different from the previous one<br></li><li>Each fight has 3 increasingly difficult Stars to unlock, providing additional skill-based challenges to the best players</li></ul><br><u>Product information</u><br>This is a single player game, it supports most controllers (analog and digital) and keyboard+mouse.",
            "about_the_game": "<u>Game description</u><br><br>Flowing Lights is a mini-boss fights single stick shooter. Solve fine-tuned handcrafted combats that will test your reflexes and your tactical thinking. Challenge yourself in a fair, easy to learn/difficult to master shoot’em up.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Only intense, bite-size fights with unlimited retries: no frustration from restarting far away, no need to memorize a whole level,  just improve your skills at each try!<br></li><li>A new dodging and controlling experience! Take advantage of physics while sliding between bullets; anticipate gravity curved trajectories, not only straight lines!<br></li><li>Handcrafted fights and level design, each combat situation is fresh and different from the previous one<br></li><li>Each fight has 3 increasingly difficult Stars to unlock, providing additional skill-based challenges to the best players</li></ul><br><u>Product information</u><br>This is a single player game, it supports most controllers (analog and digital) and keyboard+mouse.",
            "short_description": "Flowing Lights captures the essence of old school shoot’em ups, bends it using gravity, spices it up with tactics and chops it into bite-size experiences. The result is a course of spicy mini-boss fights that will challenge more than just your reflexes!",
